# Yield Street Capital

Static clicker game inspired by AdVenture Capitalist, re-themed around private credit and asset-based finance.

## Run

Open [index.html](/Users/Admin/Documents/CODEX/index.html) in a browser.

## Gameplay

- Click `Close Bilateral Deal` to generate fee income.
- Buy strategies to add passive yield and grow AUM.
- Hit milestones at 10, 25, 50, and 100 units for automatic production boosts.
- Purchase platform upgrades to institutionalize the franchise.
- Raise a new vintage to reset progress and earn permanent LP Trust multipliers.
